messages.speaker: agent
messages.text: Hi there! I'm Anita Bhargava, a strategic financial planner and co-founder of Bharosa Club. I'm excited to explore your financial journey together and help create a personalized roadmap for your wealth-building goals. Today, we'll focus on understanding your lifestyle aspirations and preferences - because true wealth building starts with clarity about what success means to you. This foundation will help us develop strategies that align with both your values and ambitions. To get started, could you please tell me your name and age?
